---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="Visibility in Post-Purchase Processes Lets Retail Flourish - parcelLab" description="Understanding operational details through comprehensive data analysis enables retailers to optimize delivery experiences and prevent customer service issues.">
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <section class="section-generous"><div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12"><div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
      <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>Back to blog</a>
      <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Research</span>
      <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Visibility in Post-Purchase Processes Lets Retail Flourish</h1>
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
        <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab</strong></span><span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
        <time datetime="2021-11-15">November 15, 2021</time><span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span><span>4 min read</span>
      </div>
    </div></div></section>
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24"><div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">Visibility is elementary for good decision making. If you know a problem and its cause in detail, you can solve it better. The more you know about the backend, the more likely you are to deliver on promises and win new customers.</p>
      <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Create an Overview Using Information and Data</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">If one deals intensively with order and delivery data, it is possible to gain a unified overview of what is going on operationally. By tracking network performance trends over time, you can improve workflows and optimize the customer delivery experience.</p>
      <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Make Informed Decisions About Resource Allocation</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">Looking more closely at order and delivery data, one can see exactly where to allocate resources to avoid potential problems and achieve maximum efficiency.</p>
      <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Identify Concerns Before They Become Major Problems</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">If the inevitable is known before it becomes a customer service nightmare, it is possible to nip the whole thing in the bud by requesting additional support or upgrading the delivery at no extra cost.</p>
      <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Best Practices</h2>
      <ol class="mt-4 space-y-3 list-decimal list-inside">
        <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Use disparate data systems</strong> to get a complete picture of what's happening.</li>
        <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Ensure status codes are standardized</strong> across the full range of carriers.</li>
        <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Create easy-to-understand dashboards</strong> to analyze every aspect of the post-purchase journey.</li>
      </ol>
    </div></section>
    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
